: 0px; color: #363636; text-decoration: none; outline: none !important;" href="http://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/11/cach-phoi-do-dep-voi-dam-trang-MANGO-overall.jpg" rel="article_gallery"><img class="wp-image-93124 size-medium" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: 490px !important; outline: none !important; display: block;" src="http://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/11/cach-phoi-do-dep-voi-dam-trang-MANGO-overall-490x685.jpg" alt="cach-phoi-do-dep-voi-dam-trang-MANGO-overall" width="490" height="685" /></a>\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 4px 5px; outline: none !important; font-style: italic; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; text-align: center;">Đầm Mango.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important;">Bạn sẽ c&oacute; được:</p>\r\n<p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important;">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div id="attachment_93123" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important; width: 500px;"><a class="auto_fancybox" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #363636; text-decoration: none; outline: none !important;" href="http://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/11/cach-phoi-do-dep-BABY-DOLL-dress.jpg" rel="article_gallery"><img class="wp-image-93123 size-medium" style="margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; max-width: 490px !important; outline: none !important; display: block;" src="http://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/11/cach-phoi-do-dep-BABY-DOLL-dress-490x692.jpg" alt="cach-phoi-do-dep-BABY-DOLL-dress" width="490" height="692" /></a>\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 4px 5px; outline: none !important; font-style: italic; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; text-align: center;">1. Đồng hồ Lacoste. 2. &Aacute;o kho&aacute;c Lacoste. 3. Mắt k&iacute;nh Topshop. 4. Vớ 