_91966" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important; width: 500px;"><a class="auto_fancybox" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #363636; text-decoration: none; outline: none !important;" href="http://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/30/cach-phoi-do-dep-gigi-daydress-mango.jpg" rel="article_gallery"><img class="wp-image-91966 size-medium" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 490px !important; height: auto; vertical-align: middle; border: none; outline: none !important;" src="http://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/30/cach-phoi-do-dep-gigi-daydress-mango-490x685.jpg" alt="cach-phoi-do-dep-gigi-daydress-mango" width="490" height="685" /></a>\r\n<p class="wp-caption-text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 4px 4px 5px; outline: none !important; font-style: italic; font-size: 13px; line-height: 17px; text-align: center;">Đầm Mango</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important;">6. Những m&oacute;n phụ kiện kh&ocirc;ng thể thiếu</strong></p>\r\n<p style="margin: 20px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important;">Với k&iacute;nh m&aacute;t,&nbsp;Gigi thường chọn mắt k&iacute;nh mặt gương c&oacute; kiểu d&aacute;ng mắt m&egrave;o hay bầu tr&ograve;n. Kiểu gi&agrave;y ankle boots v&agrave; gi&agrave;y cao g&oacute;t (pump) kiểu d&aacute;ng đơn giản, gi&agrave;y sneaker thể thao m&agrave;u hoặc trắng cũng l&agrave; những m&oacute;n phụ kiện kh&ocirc;ng thể thiếu đối với Gigi.</p>\r\n<div id="attachment_91962" class="wp-caption alignnone" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: none !important; width: 500px;"><a class="auto_fancybox" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #363636; text-decoration: none; outline: none !important;" href="http://www.elle.vn/wp-content/uploads/2015/07/30/cach-phoi-do-dep-gigi-accessories2.jpg" rel="article_gallery"><img class="wp-image-91962 size-medium" style="margi